Roomedit

You may edit your homeroom using `roomedit', but you must be in your 
homeroom to use this command.  IMMs may also use this command to edit 
the room in which they are currently located.  

Roomedit uses SMUD's inbuilt editor:

Editor Commands:
.quit   - Quit and abandon changes.
.end    - Quit and save changes.
.stats  - Current buffer stats.
.del    - Delete current line.
.wipe   - Wipes whole buffer.
.+      - Next line.
.-      - Previous line.
.view   - Output current buffer.
